description:
Videoartista e fotógrafo, desenvolve projetos nos campos da
arquitetura, do cinema, do teatro e das artes visuais. Atualmente,
encontra-se engajado no registro fotográfico e audiovisual do
processo de reforma do Estádio do Pacaembu, em São Paulo. Em
2022, em parceria Ubiratan Suruí, foi responsável
pela captação de imagens e edição do conteúdo das projeções
do espetáculo “Amazonias - Ver a Mata que te Vê”, produzido pelo Sesc São Paulo.
Em 2021, co-dirigiu com Maria Thais o longa-metragem “Territórios
de Resistência: Florestanias - Sertanias - Ribeirias”, disponível nas
plataformas Sesc Digital e SescTv. Ainda em 2021, realizou um
ensaio audiovisual e fotográfico para o website do Instituto
Bardi/Casa de Vidro. Em 2020, co-dirigiu com Maria Thais o
videoclipe do novo arranjo da canção “Paratodos”, de Chico Buarque
para o Sesc SP e Museu do Ipiranga. Em 2013, formou-se em Cinema
pela FAAP com o curta-metragem “Noite na Taverna”.

description:
Aditya Varma is a director of photography and photographer from Mumbai.
His two full length feature films, 'Namdev Bhau in Search of Silence' (dir. Daria Gai) and 'Kia and Cosmos' (dir. Sudipto Roy),  Both of the films have  travelled to various international film festivals and he was nominated for best cinematography in Milan and Nice International Fim Festivals for 'Kia and Cosmos'. 
He has also been the stills photographer for 'Manto' (dir. Nandita Das), which was showcased at Cannes Film Festival in Un Certain Regard section. He has shot and edited over twenty advertisements for leading companies and fashion campaigns for national and international brands including promotionals for Bumble, Netflix, Jio. He shot music videos for musicians like Prateek Kuhad, Ritviz, Jasleen Royal, Vayu, Hanita Bhambri. He shoots documentaries as well, the most recent of which is a travel show following leading bikers of India called "Cruising Legends". He is currently working on a web series.

description:
When I was a young boy (1950's), I learned to play golf by closely watching the best players at the course I grew up on. I would then stand in front of a window and copy their swings... then I would go to the practice area to ingrain that look and new feeling to muscle memory. That WAS and STILL IS a great way to learn! It's called SELF-DISCOVERY! 

When you discover a helpful motion or thought ALL BY YOURSELF, YOU WILL NEVER FORGET IT! - I never have!  

At the age of 78, I'm still a mid single-digit player. My goal with this YouTube channel is to provide a platform for TEACHING and LEARNING! I will provide videos and detailed descriptions of the finest golfers in the world, their swings and some of their finest shots so YOU can learn and improve as I have. 

The focus here is geared toward TEACHING and LEARNING the short game (putting, chipping, pitching and wedge play from 120-yards in), but you will also see some of the finest, Tour-Proven full swings and descriptions as well.⛳️

Компания была основана в 2010 году. Начиналось все с разработки Android-прошивки MIUI. В штат компании на ранних этапах вошли специалисты из Google, Kingsoft, Microsoft, Motorola, Yahoo.

Ассортимент постоянно расширяется, продукция учитывает требования рынка и пожелания пользователей.

Кстати, в логотипе «Mi» зашифровано словосочетание «Мобильный Интернет». Но есть и второе значение, которое звучит как «Миссия Невыполнима» (Mission Impossible). Xiaomi продолжает доказывать, что миссия выполнима, а инновации должны быть доступны каждому!

description: Видеосъёмка , монтаж , фотография - уже много лет любимые увлечения . Фотографирую с начала 80-х : начинал  с "Зенитом-Е" , видео снимаю с 96-го : начинал с "Panasonic-3500" . Был ИП с 96 года : снимал торжества и мероприятия ,  работал в ДК Молодечно с его открытия в 2002 : руководителем видеостудии , техником по видеооборудованию , оператором , инженером видеомонтажа  , до 2021 года . Пробовал себя на Молодечненском ТВ оператором с 2004 по 2007.   Сейчас   зарегистрирован в налоговой с оплатой НПД  . Есть Sony A6400 + 18-135 mm , вспышка , свет , петлица , Rode SVM . Фотографирую , снимаю видео , оцифровываю старые видеокассеты , занимаюсь монтажом фото и видео (не только своего) . На канале - мероприятия , видео для души , старые  съёмки , ролики из фотографий и всякое-разное . Для удобства  раскидал на плейлисты . Найти меня можно и в инстаграм  , там фото и видео природы , людей , домашних питомцев - в общем всего понемногу...

I started a street photography project on my Instagram to show my point of view, when I take photos of strangers and when I do candid street photography and film photography.

I will share my street photography tips and tricks on this channel and hopefully learn a lot more about portrait photography and storytelling through photography.

Most of my street portraits are shot in black and white and when I take photos of strangers in public, it's a mix of candid and with permission.

description:
Hello everyone. I am a new pigeon fancier who started raising and breeding pigeons in summer of 2018. I started by only having pairs of show birds but i quickly changed my focus to racing pigeons and am now working on acquiring and breeding the best birds that i can so that hopefully by the year 2020, i will be able to start racing my birds. My loft is 10 feet by 10 feet and it is roughly 7 and a half feet tall and is split into 2 almost equal sections (racing and breeding). For the time being, i have plenty of room for 12 breeding pairs and i plan on having somewhere around 40 racing birds.

UPDATE: With the coronavirus taking over the world, nobody knows what will happen with this racing season. Right now i have 18 breeding pairs (12 here and 6 at my fathers loft) and it is looking like i will finish the breeding season with roughly 60-65 young birds.

What is a PTZ Camera?
A PTZ camera is a pan, tilt, and zoom robotic video camera controllable by a remote operator to pan horizontally, tilt vertically & diagonally, and zoom in on a subject to enhance the image quality without digital pixilation. These cameras are designed to make broadcast-quality video affordable. They allow for an easy, automated production workflow with other software technologies for recording and live streaming directly to content delivery networks like Facebook and YouTube.

PTZOptics is a broadcast, live streaming and conference camera manufacturer operating out of Downingtown, Pennsylvania, USA. We provide Pan Tilt Zoom Cameras with HDMI, HD-SDI, USB 3.0 and IP Streaming at resolutions up to 1080p60fps for the professional broadcast and video conferencing markets.
